sequenceDiagram
    participant C as 客户端
    participant A as 接入服务
    participant R as Redis
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant O as 订单消费者
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant X as Outbox Relay

    C->>A: request_id秒杀请求
    A->>A: 生成reservation_id和固定message_id
    A->>R: Lua预占并写reservation、待发送ZSET
    R-->>A: RESERVED

    A->>M: ORDER_CREATE_REQUESTED
    M-->>A: Send ACK
    A->>R: mq_state=PUBLISHED
    A-->>C: QUEUED

    M->>O: 投递消息
    O->>P: BEGIN
    O->>P: INSERT consumer_inbox
    O->>P: 锁定/创建inventory_reservation
    O->>P: 条件扣减最终库存
    O->>P: INSERT orders
    O->>P: INSERT inventory_ledger
    O->>P: INSERT event_outbox
    O->>P: COMMIT
    O-->>M: Consume ACK

    X->>P: 领取ORDER_CREATED Outbox
    X->>M: 发送订单创建事件
    M->>R: 更新Redis查询投影
